source.name: Storm Events Database
source.description: Search the NCDC Storm Events Database to find various types of storms recorded in your county. The database currently contains data from 1999 to Present, as entered by NOAA's National Weather Service (NWS). NOTE: This data is being updated and will eventually (summer 2013) contain data from 1950-current.
